{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Chapter Marker Updater for Audiobooks\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The script, updates the PROJECT_NAME.SideCar.txt file, when markers are renamed and/or moved. Just calling the script, it remove the old file, with a new updated one.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Once done, it returns a popup window that informs the users, that everything is perfectly done.\par}
}

